import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    group_counts = data.groupby('group').count()['person']
    plt.bar(group_counts.index, group_counts.values, color=['#1f77b4', '#ff7f0e', '#2ca02c'])
    plt.title('What is the distribution of people across the groups?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Group ID')
    plt.ylabel('Count of People')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.style.use('ggplot')
    plt.figure(figsize=(8,6))
    person_count = data.groupby('person').size().reset_index(name='count')
    person_count.plot(kind='bar', x='person', y='count', legend=False, color='blue')
    plt.xlabel('Person Name')
    plt.ylabel('Count')
    plt.title('What is the most common name among the people in the groups?', wrap=True)
    plt.xticks(rotation=0)
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data.groupby('group').count()['person'], bins=3, color='green')
    plt.axvline(data.groupby('group').count()['person'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label='Mean')
    plt.legend(loc='upper right')
    plt.title('What is the average number of people in each group?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Number of people in each group')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    return plt

data = pd.read_csv('lookup_groups.csv')
chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    group_counts = data['group'].value_counts()
    ax = group_counts.plot(kind='bar', color='blue')
    ax.set_xlabel('Group ID')
    ax.set_ylabel('Count')
    ax.axhline(y=group_counts.max(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f'Most common group ID: {group_counts.idxmax()} ({group_counts.max()} members)')
    ax.legend()
    plt.title('What is the most common group ID?', wrap=True)
    return plt

data = pd.read_csv('lookup_groups.csv')
chart = plot(data)
```
